<div class="jumbotron">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align: center">
      <h1 class="display-3 text-primary">BC Open Source Month</h1>
      <p class="lead">A month-long open source competition for students in British Columbia, hosted by <a href="https://www.startupstorm.org">StartupStorm</a>, and inspired by <a href="https://hacktoberfest.digitalocean.com">Hacktoberfest</a>.</p>
    <hr class="my-4">
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="width: 100%;">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title">How does this work?</h4>
      <!-- <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Card subtitle</h6> -->
      <p class="card-text">Take some time this month to get involved with open source development on GitHub - as you make more contributions to external projects, you and your school's score will increase in the leaderboard below.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="width: 100%;">
    <div class="card-body">
      <h4 class="card-title">What if I'm new to open source?</h4>
      <!-- <h6 class="card-subtitle mb-2 text-muted">Card subtitle</h6> -->
      <p class="card-text">No problem! <a href="http://www.github.com">Create a GitHub account</a> and follow the <a href="https://opensource.guide/how-to-contribute/">official open source guide.</a></p>
    </div>
  </div>


			<% if (!user) { %>
